{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01SH9ELiqXgDGgFXMgUxMPfJ","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Let me provide a comprehensive overview of the codebase:\n\nProject Structure Overview:\n- This is a Quarkus-based Coffee Shop Management Application\n- Build System: Maven (pom.xml)\n- Java Version: 17\n- Framework: Quarkus 3.30.5\n\nKey Architectural Components:\n1. Domains:\n   - Order Management\n   - Barista Operations\n   - Kitchen Management\n   - Counter/Order Placement\n\nMain Technologies and Frameworks:\n- Quarkus\n- Hibernate ORM with Panache\n- PostgreSQL Database\n- Kafka Messaging\n- RESTful Web Services\n- JUnit 5 for Testing\n- Mutiny for Reactive Programming\n\nKey Components:\n1. Domains:\n   - `io.quarkuscoffeeshop.coffeeshop.domain`\n     - Order, OrderIn, OrderStatus, LineItem\n     - Location, Item, Beverage, ItemStatus\n\n2. Infrastructure:\n   - Multiple datasources (main, barista, kitchen)\n   - Supports dev (H2), test (PostgreSQL), and prod environments\n   - Kafka messaging for event-driven architecture\n\n3. Web Layer:\n   - `CoffeeshopApiResource`: Main API endpoints\n   - `DashboardEndpoint`: Real-time dashboard\n   - SSE (Server-Sent Events) for streaming updates\n\n4. Business Logic:\n   - Barista service\n   - Kitchen service\n   - Order service\n   - Repositories for data persistence\n\nDeployment and Configuration:\n- Docker support with multiple Dockerfiles\n- Environment-driven configuration\n- Supports native compilation\n- Comprehensive logging configuration\n\nUnique Features:\n- Multi-schema database support\n- Event-driven microservices architecture\n- Reactive programming with Mutiny\n- Extensive testing infrastructure\n\nDevelopment Extras:\n- PMD and SpotBugs for code quality\n- JaCoCo for test coverage\n- Comprehensive CORS configuration\n- Playwright for browser testing\n\nWould you like me to dive deeper into any specific aspect of this codebase?"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a1c50a88-828f-43a6-8dbe-524f630482b2","uuid":"fa1c960b-0bea-4362-aeb2-e20978c002ec"}
