Or let us know what you thought about the demo?</p>\n   885→            </div>\n   886→        </div>\n   887→        <div class=\"row\">\n   888→            <div class=\"col-xs-12 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2\">\n   889→                <form>\n   890→                    <div class=\"form-group col-md-6\">\n   891→                        <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Name\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"name\">\n   892→                    </div>\n   893→                    <div class=\"form-group col-md-6\">\n   894→                        <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Email\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"email\">\n   895→                    </div>\n   896→                    <div class=\"form-group col-xs-12\">\n   897→                        <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Subject\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"subject\">\n   898→                    </div>\n   899→                    <div class=\"form-group col-xs-12\">\n   900→                        <textarea class=\"form-control\" placeholder=\"How can we help you?\" rows=\"6\" id=\"message\"></textarea>\n   901→                    </div>\n   902→                    <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn btn-default\">Submit</button>\n   903→                </form>\n   904→            </div>\n   905→        </div>\n   906→        <div class=\"row contact-boxes\">\n   907→            <div class=\"col-lg-4\">\n   908→                <div class=\"box wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-duration=\"400ms\" data-wow-offset=\"10\">\n   909→                    <i class=\"fa fa-map-marker\"></i>\n   910→                    <h6>Visit With Us</h6>\n   911→                    <p><a href=\"https://quarkus.io\">Quarkus.io</a></p>\n   912→                </div>\n   913→            </div>\n   914→            <div class=\"col-lg-4\">\n   915→                <div class=\"box wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-duration=\"800ms\" data-wow-offset=\"10\">\n   916→                    <i class=\"fa fa-phone\"></i>\n   917→                    <h6>Get In Touch</h6>\n   918→                    <p><a href=\"https://quarkusio.zulipchat.com\" >Quarkus Zulip Chat</a></p>\n   919→                    <p><a href=\"https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/quarkus-dev\">Google Groups</a></p>\n   920→                </div>\n   921→            </div>\n   922→            <div class=\"col-lg-4\">\n   923→                <div class=\"box wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-duration=\"1.2s\" data-wow-offset=\"10\">\n   924→                    <i class=\"fa fa-clock-o\"></i>\n   925→                    <h6>Hours of Operation</h6>\n   926→                    <p>Monday-Friday: 9am-7pm<br />\n   927→                        Saturday &amp; Sunday: 8am-8pm\n   928→                    </p>\n   929→                </div>\n   930→            </div>\n   931→        </div>\n   932→    </div>\n   933→</section>\n   934→<section class=\"footer\">\n   935→    <div class=\"container\">\n   936→        <div class=\"row\">\n   937→            <div class=\"col-xs-12\">\n   938→                <ul class=\"list-inline text-center margin-bottom\">\n   939→                    <li><a href=\"\"><i class=\"fa fa-facebook\"></i></a></li>\n   940→                    <li><a href=\"\"><i class=\"fa fa-twitter\"></i></a></li>\n   941→                    <li><a href=\"\"><i class=\"fa fa-linkedin\"></i></a></li>\n   942→                    <li><a href=\"\"><i class=\"fa fa-behance\"></i></a></li>\n   943→                </ul>\n   944→                <p class=\"text-center\">© 2018 <a href=\"http://hh-themes.com/\" target=\"_blank\">HH Themes</a></p>\n   945→                <!-- Please do not remove the backlink to us unless you have purchased a license. It is part of the license conditions. Thanks for understanding :) -->\n   946→            </div>\n   947→        </div>\n   948→    </div>\n   949→    <div id=\"back-to-top\"><i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-up\"></i></div>\n   950→</section>\n   951→<div class=\".d-none\"></div>\n   952→<appvalues id=\"appvalues\"\n   953→        