aceOrderCommand)` and `void onOrderUp(String message)` (String instead of Message)\n\n5. **OrderServiceImpl.java** (src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/counter/OrderServiceImpl.java)\n   - Was: `@ApplicationScoped` with Vert.x EventBus, `@ConsumeEvent`, `@Blocking`\n   - Should be: `@Service` with Spring's `ApplicationEventPublisher` for web updates, and direct method calls.\n   - Replace `eventBus.publish(WEB_UPDATES, ...)` with `applicationEventPublisher.publishEvent(new WebUpdateEvent(...))`\n   - Replace `eventBus.send(BARISTA_IN, ...)` with `applicationEventPublisher.publishEvent(new BaristaInEvent(...))`\n   - Replace `eventBus.send(KITCHEN_IN, ...)` with `applicationEventPublisher.publishEvent(new KitchenInEvent(...))`\n   - Keep `@Transactional` (from jakarta.transaction)\n   - The `onOrderUp` method should take a String (JSON) parameter instead of Message\n\n6. **Barista.java** interface (src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/barista/api/Barista.java)\n   - Was: interface with Message parameter\n   - Should be: interface with `void onOrderIn(String orderInJson)`\n\n7. **BaristaImpl.java** (src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/barista/BaristaImpl.java)\n   - Was: commented out `@ApplicationScoped` with `@ConsumeEvent`\n   - Keep as-is functionality but don't add Spring annotations since it was commented out in original. Just make it a plain class with no Quarkus imports.\n\n8. **BaristaOutpostImpl.java** (src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/barista/BaristaOutpostImpl.java)\n   - Was: `@Startup @ApplicationScoped` with `@ConsumeEvent(BARISTA_IN)` and `@Incoming(\"orders-up\")` for Kafka\n   - Should be: `@Service` with `@EventListener` for BARISTA_IN events, and `@KafkaListener` for orders-up topic\n   - For outgoing Kafka, use `KafkaTemplate<String, String>` instead of SmallRye Emitter\n   - For the `@Incoming(\"orders-up\")` method, use Spring Kafka `@KafkaListener(topics = \"orders-up\")`\n   - Publishing ORDERS_UP events should use `applicationEventPublisher.publishEvent(new OrdersUpEvent(...))`\n\n9. **Kitchen.java** interface (src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/kitchen/Kitchen.java)\n   - Should be: `void onOrderIn(String message)`\n\n10. **KitchenImpl.java** (src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/kitchen/KitchenImpl.java)\n    - Was: `@ApplicationScoped` with `@ConsumeEvent(KITCHEN_IN)`, Vert.x EventBus\n    - Should be: `@Service` with `@EventListener` for KitchenInEvent, Spring `ApplicationEventPublisher`\n\n11. **CoffeeshopApiResource.java** (src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/web/CoffeeshopApiResource.java)\n    - Was: JAX-RS `@Path(\"/api\")` with `@POST @Path(\"/order\")`\n    - Should be: Spring MVC `@RestController @RequestMapping(\"/api\")` with `@PostMapping(\"/order\")`\n    - Replace `jakarta.ws.rs.*` imports with Spring Web imports\n    - Replace `Response.accepted().build()` with `ResponseEntity.accepted().build()`\n    - For sendMessage endpoint: use `ApplicationEventPublisher` instead of EventBus\n\n12. **DashboardEndpoint.java** (src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/web/DashboardEndpoint.java)\n    - Was: JAX-RS SSE with Mutiny Multi and Vert.x EventBus consumer\n    - Should be: Spring SSE with `SseEmitter`. Create a `@RestController` with `@GetMapping(\"/dashboard/stream\")` that returns `SseEmitter`. Keep a list of active emitters and send events to them.\n\n13. **WebResource.java** (src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/web/WebResource.java)\n    - Was: Qute template with `@ConfigProperty`\n    - Should be: Spring MVC `@Controller` with `@Value` annotations and Thymeleaf `Model`\n    - Return a string template name \"coffeeshopTemplate\" and populate model attributes\n\n14. **EventBusTopics.java** (src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/infrastructure/EventBusTopics.java)\n    - Keep as-is (it's just constants)\n\n15. **JsonUtil.java** (src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/utils/JsonUtil.java)\n    - Keep