{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01XVC1ogVPPPmAEN3mjFzkCZ","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! All files have been migrated. Let me create a summary of all the changes:\n\n## Migration Summary\n\nI have successfully migrated all 21 files from Quarkus to Spring Boot 3.2.5. Here's a detailed breakdown of the changes:\n\n### Repositories (3 files) - Spring Data JPA\nAll three repositories have been converted from Quarkus Panache to Spring Data JPA:\n\n1. **BaristaRepository.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/barista/domain/BaristaRepository.java`)\n   - Changed from `@ApplicationScoped` class implementing `PanacheRepository<BaristaItem>` \n   - To `@Repository` interface extending `JpaRepository<BaristaItem, Long>`\n   - Removed Agroal datasource injection\n\n2. **KitchenOrderRepository.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/kitchen/domain/KitchenOrderRepository.java`)\n   - Changed from `@ApplicationScoped` class implementing `PanacheRepository<KitchenOrder>`\n   - To `@Repository` interface extending `JpaRepository<KitchenOrder, Long>`\n   - Removed Agroal datasource injection\n\n3. **OrderRepository.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/infrastructure/OrderRepository.java`)\n   - Changed from `@ApplicationScoped` class implementing `PanacheRepository<Order>`\n   - To `@Repository` interface extending `JpaRepository<Order, String>`\n   - Added `findByOrderId(String orderId)` method\n\n### Service Layer (2 files)\n\n4. **OrderService.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/counter/api/OrderService.java`)\n   - Changed from Vert.x `Message` parameters to plain String\n   - Signatures: `void onOrderIn(PlaceOrderCommand)` and `void onOrderUp(String message)`\n\n5. **OrderServiceImpl.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/counter/OrderServiceImpl.java`)\n   - Changed from `@ApplicationScoped` to `@Service`\n   - Replaced Vert.x EventBus with Spring's `ApplicationEventPublisher`\n   - Replaced `@ConsumeEvent` with `@EventListener`\n   - Replaced `eventBus.publish(WEB_UPDATES, ...)` with `applicationEventPublisher.publishEvent(new WebUpdateEvent(...))`\n   - Replaced `eventBus.send(BARISTA_IN, ...)` with `applicationEventPublisher.publishEvent(new BaristaInEvent(...))`\n   - Replaced `eventBus.send(KITCHEN_IN, ...)` with `applicationEventPublisher.publishEvent(new KitchenInEvent(...))`\n   - Changed `persist()` to `save()` for repository operations\n\n### Barista Components (3 files)\n\n6. **Barista.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/barista/api/Barista.java`)\n   - Changed from Vert.x `Message` parameter to `String orderInJson`\n\n7. **BaristaImpl.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/barista/BaristaImpl.java`)\n   - Kept as plain class (no Spring annotations, as it was commented out in original)\n   - Removed all Quarkus imports\n   - Changed `persist()` to `save()`\n\n8. **BaristaOutpostImpl.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/barista/BaristaOutpostImpl.java`)\n   - Changed from `@Startup @ApplicationScoped` to `@Service`\n   - Replaced `@ConsumeEvent(BARISTA_IN)` with `@EventListener(BaristaInEvent.class)`\n   - Replaced SmallRye `@Incoming(\"orders-up\")` with `@KafkaListener(topics = \"orders-up\", autoStartup = \"${kafka.enabled:false}\")`\n   - Replaced SmallRye `Emitter` with Spring `KafkaTemplate<String, String>`\n   - Made Kafka optional with `@Autowired(required = false)`\n   - Replaced `eventBus.publish(ORDERS_UP, ...)` with `applicationEventPublisher.publishEvent(new OrdersUpEvent(...))`\n\n### Kitchen Components (2 files)\n\n9. **Kitchen.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/kitchen/Kitchen.java`)\n   - Changed from Vert.x `Message` parameter to `String message`\n\n10. **KitchenImpl.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/kitchen/KitchenImpl.java`)\n    - Changed from `@ApplicationScoped` to `@Service`\n    - Replaced Vert.x EventBus with Spring's `ApplicationEventPublisher`\n    - Replaced `@ConsumeEvent(KITCHEN_IN)` with `@EventListener(KitchenInEvent.class)`\n    - Replaced `eventBus.publish(ORDERS_UP, ...)` with `applicationEventPublisher.publishEvent(new OrdersUpEvent(...))`\n    - Changed `persist()` to `save()`\n\n### Web Controllers (3 files)\n\n11. **CoffeeshopApiResource.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/web/CoffeeshopApiResource.java`)\n    - Changed from JAX-RS `@Path(\"/api\")` to Spring MVC `@RestController @RequestMapping(\"/api\")`\n    - Replaced `@POST @Path(\"/order\")` with `@PostMapping(\"/order\")`\n    - Replaced JAX-RS imports (`jakarta.ws.rs.*`) with Spring Web imports\n    - Replaced `Response.accepted().build()` with `ResponseEntity.accepted().build()`\n    - Replaced EventBus with `ApplicationEventPublisher`\n\n12. **DashboardEndpoint.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/web/DashboardEndpoint.java`)\n    - Changed from JAX-RS SSE with Mutiny Multi to Spring `SseEmitter`\n    - Changed from `@Path(\"/dashboard\")` to `@RestController @RequestMapping(\"/dashboard\")`\n    - Replaced Vert.x EventBus consumer with DashboardService that manages emitters\n    - Returns `SseEmitter` from `@GetMapping(\"/stream\")`\n\n13. **WebResource.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/web/WebResource.java`)\n    - Changed from Qute template to Thymeleaf\n    - Changed from `@Path(\"/\")` to `@Controller @GetMapping(\"/\")`\n    - Replaced `@ConfigProperty` with `@Value`\n    - Replaced `Template` and `TemplateInstance` with Spring `Model`\n    - Returns template name \"coffeeshopTemplate\" instead of TemplateInstance\n\n### Supporting Files (2 files kept as-is)\n\n14. **EventBusTopics.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/infrastructure/EventBusTopics.java`)\n    - No changes needed (just constants)\n\n15. **JsonUtil.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/utils/JsonUtil.java`)\n    - No changes needed (no Quarkus-specific code)\n\n### New Event Classes (4 files created)\n\n16. **WebUpdateEvent.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/infrastructure/events/WebUpdateEvent.java`)\n    - Simple event class with String payload\n\n17. **BaristaInEvent.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/infrastructure/events/BaristaInEvent.java`)\n    - Simple event class with String payload\n\n18. **KitchenInEvent.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/infrastructure/events/KitchenInEvent.java`)\n    - Simple event class with String payload\n\n19. **OrdersUpEvent.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/infrastructure/events/OrdersUpEvent.java`)\n    - Simple event class with String payload\n\n### New Service Classes (2 files created)\n\n20. **DashboardService.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/web/DashboardService.java`)\n    - `@Service` class with `@EventListener` for `WebUpdateEvent`\n    - Maintains `CopyOnWriteArrayList<SseEmitter>` for active SSE connections\n    - Broadcasts updates to all connected clients\n    - Provides `registerEmitter(SseEmitter)` method\n\n21. **KafkaConfig.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/infrastructure/KafkaConfig.java`)\n    - `@Configuration` with `@ConditionalOnProperty(name = \"spring.kafka.bootstrap-servers\")`\n    - Makes Kafka optional - only active when bootstrap servers are configured\n\n## Key Architecture Changes\n\n1. **Event System**: Replaced Vert.x EventBus with Spring's `ApplicationEventPublisher` pattern\n2. **Persistence**: Changed from Panache to Spring Data JPA repositories\n3. **Dependency Injection**: Replaced CDI (`@Inject`, `@ApplicationScoped`) with Spring (`@Autowired`, `@Service`, `@Repository`)\n4. **REST Layer**: Migrated from JAX-RS to Spring MVC\n5. **Messaging**: Replaced SmallRye Reactive Messaging with Spring Kafka (made optional)\n6. **SSE**: Replaced Mutiny Multi with Spring's SseEmitter\n7. **Templates**: Prepared for Thymeleaf (changed from Qute)\n8. **Transactions**: Kept `@Transactional` from jakarta.transaction\n\nAll files have been successfully migrated and are ready for Spring Boot 3.2.5!"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a1c50a88-828f-43a6-8dbe-524f630482b2","uuid":"8d5737a1-f38c-47b2-994f-eca7572a4b27"}
