{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01WmjPycjCdgeDajWtdPXoXu","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→<!DOCTYPE html>\n     2→<html lang=\"en\">\n     3→<head>\n     4→    <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n     5→    <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n     6→    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n     7→    <meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\">\n     8→    <!-- The above 3 meta tags *must* come first in the head; any other head content must come *after* these tags -->\n     9→    <title>Quarkus Coffee Shop</title>\n    10→    <link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" sizes=\"180x180\" href=\"favicon/apple-touch-icon.png\">\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a1c50a88-828f-43a6-8dbe-524f630482b2","uuid":"a8e67d21-ddf6-458e-9e48-13c0b1c31027"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_011Bxw4mRLGUG2CRmfP74xGc","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→FROM maven:3.9.12-ibm-semeru-21-noble\n     2→\n     3→USER root\n     4→# install uv\n     5→RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends curl lsof python3-venv python3-full     && curl -LsSf https://astral.sh/uv/install.sh | sh\n     6→\n     7→ENV PATH=\"/root/.local/bin:$PATH\"\n     8→\n     9→# Shared browsers path so Chromium is cached once\n    10→ENV PLAYWRIGHT_BROWSERS_PATH=/ms-playwright\n    11→RUN mkdir -p /ms-playwright && chmod 755 /ms-playwright\n    12→\n    13→# create venv and install\n    14→RUN uv venv /opt/venv     && uv pip install --python /opt/venv/bin/python playwright==1.47.0 pytest\n    15→\n    16→ENV PATH=\"/opt/venv/bin:$PATH\"\n    17→RUN playwright install --with-deps chromium\n    18→\n    19→# Set working directory\n    20→WORKDIR /app\n    21→\n    22→# Copy all the assets\n    23→COPY . .\n    24→\n    25→# Build the application at image build time\n    26→RUN mvn clean package -DskipTests -Dpmd.skip=true -Dspotbugs.skip=true\n    27→\n    28→CMD [\"mvn\", \"quarkus:dev\", \"-Dquarkus.analytics.disabled=true\", \"-Dpmd.skip=true\", \"-Dspotbugs.skip=true\"]\n    29→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a1c50a88-828f-43a6-8dbe-524f630482b2","uuid":"18353162-f190-40af-962b-faafd2e84a39"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01TY4oeC71zDLkePLGmCSnKd","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me write the updated template and Dockerfile:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1040,"cache_read_input_tokens":102473,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1040,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":5436},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a1c50a88-828f-43a6-8dbe-524f630482b2","uuid":"ac2ca772-b144-43ee-a569-60c03d4e2254"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01TY4oeC71zDLkePLGmCSnKd","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01SBC9fk8ZTbG3bvmFPUXnkU","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/resources/templates/coffeeshopTemplate.html","content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\" xmlns:th=\"http://www.thymeleaf.org\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n    <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n    <meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\">\n    <title>Coffee Shop</title>\n    <link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" sizes=\"180x180\" href=\"/favicon/apple-touch-icon.png\">\n    <link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/png\" sizes=\"32x32\" href=\"/favicon/favicon-32x32.png\">\n    <link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/png\" sizes=\"16x16\" href=\"/favicon/favicon-16x16.png\">\n    <link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"/favicon/favicon.ico\">\n    <link href=\"/css/bootstrap.min.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link href=\"/css/styles.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link href=\"/css/custom.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Cookie%7cMontserrat:300,400,500,600,700%7cRoboto:300,400,500,700\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link href=\"https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" integrity=\"sha384-wvfXpqpZZVQGK6TAh5PVlGOfQNHSoD2xbE+QkPxCAFlNEevoEH3Sl0sibVcOQVnN\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/3.5.2/animate.min.css\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/ekko-lightbox/5.3.0/ekko-lightbox.css\">\n    <link href=\"/css/cafe.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" />\n    <link href=\"/css/toastr.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n</head>\n<body>\n<nav class=\"navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark fixed-top\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <a class=\"navbar-brand\" href=\"#banner\"><i class=\"fa fa-coffee\"></i> Coffee Shop</a>\n    <button class=\"navbar-toggler\" type=\"button\"\n            data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#navbarSupportedContent\"\n            aria-controls=\"navbarSupportedContent\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Toggle navigation\">\n      <span class=\"navbar-toggler-icon\"></span>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"collapse navbar-collapse\" id=\"navbarSupportedContent\">\n      <ul class=\"navbar-nav ms-auto mb-2 mb-lg-0\">\n        <li class=\"nav-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"#about\">About</a></li>\n        <li class=\"nav-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"#menu\">Menu</a></li>\n        <li class=\"nav-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"#gallery\">Gallery</a></li>\n        <li class=\"nav-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"#team\">Team</a></li>\n        <li class=\"nav-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"#testimonials\">Twitter</a></li>\n        <li class=\"nav-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n        <li id=\"rewards_link\" class=\"nav-item\">\n          <a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"#\" data-bs-toggle=\"modal\" data-bs-target=\"#rewardsModal\">Rewards</a>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</nav>\n\n<span id=\"banner\"></span>\n<section class=\"banner\">\n    <div class=\"jumbotron\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"content\">\n                <h5>Established 2020</h5>\n                <h1>Coffee Shop</h1>\n                <a href=\"#menu\" class=\"btn\">Place an Order</a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n\n<div class=\"modal\" id=\"rewardsModal\">\n    <div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n        <form id=\"rewards_modal\">\n            <div class=\"modal-content\">\n                <div class=\"modal-header\">\n                    <h4 class=\"modal-title\">Rewards Info</h4>\n                    <button id=\"btn_cancel\" type=\"button\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" aria-label=\"Close\"></button>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"modal-body flex-fill d-inline-flex\">\n                    <div class=\"flex-fill d-inline-flex justify-content-end form-group\">\n                        <label for=\"rewards_id\" class=\"mr-sm-2 input-cafe text-nowrap mb-2\">Rewards email:</label>\n                        <input type=\"email\" required class=\"form-control mb-2 mr-sm-2\" placeholder=\"Enter rewards email\" id=\"rewards_id\" rewards_id=\"rewards_id\">\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"modal-footer\">\n                    <div class=\"flex-fill\">\n                        <button type=\"submit\" id=\"rewards_entered\" class=\"btn-sm btn-primary pull-right\">Done</button>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </form>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n<span class=\"anchor\" id=\"about\"></span>\n<section class=\"about\">\n    <div class=\"container padding-2x\">\n        <div class=\"row text-wrap\">\n            <div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n                <h3 class=\"text-center\">Welcome to Coffee Shop</h3>\n                <hr>\n                <p class=\"text-center\">A demo application showcasing an event driven architecture.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"row about-info\">\n            <div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6\">\n                <div class=\"box wow fadeIn\" data-wow-duration=\"400ms\" data-wow-offset=\"10\">\n                    <img src=\"/images/about.jpg\" alt=\"about\" />\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6\">\n                <div class=\"box wow fadeIn\" data-wow-duration=\"800ms\" data-wow-offset=\"10\">\n                    <h5>Our Story</h5>\n                    <p>This application is a demo showcasing an event driven application that uses messaging for communication.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n<span class=\"anchor\" id=\"menu\"></span>\n<section class=\"menu\">\n    <div class=\"container padding-2x\">\n        <div class=\"row text-wrap\">\n            <div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n                <h3 class=\"text-center\">Menu</h3>\n                <hr>\n                <p class=\"text-center\">Choose your items below.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"modal\" id=\"myModal\">\n            <div class=\"modal-dialog\" display=\"flex\">\n                <div class=\"modal-content\">\n                    <div class=\"modal-header\">\n                        <h4 class=\"modal-title\">Current Order</h4>\n                        <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" aria-label=\"Close\"></button>\n                        <div class=\"pt-10\">\n                            <ul class=\"list-group mt-10\" id=\"current_order\"></ul>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"alert alert-success\" role=\"alert\" id=\"item_added_alert\"></div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"modal-body\">\n                        <div id=\"rewards_display\" class=\"small text-muted\" style=\"align-self: flex-end\">\n                            <text>Rewards member</text>\n                            <text id=\"rewards_display_id\"></text>\n                        </div>\n                        <form class=\"form-inline\" action=\"\" id=\"item_form\">\n                            <div class=\"flex-fill d-inline-flex justify-content-between\">\n                                <input type=\"hidden\" id=\"item_type\" name=\"item_type\"/>\n                                <input type=\"hidden\" id=\"item_price\" name=\"item_price\"/>\n                                <label for=\"item\" class=\"mr-sm-2 input-cafe text-nowrap mb-2\" id=\"item_label\"></label>\n                                <input type=\"hidden\" id=\"item\" name=\"item\"/>\n                                <label for=\"name\" class=\"mr-sm-2 input-cafe text-nowrap mb-2\">for Name:</label>\n                                <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control mb-2 mr-sm-2\" placeholder=\"Enter name\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\">\n                                <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn-sm btn-primary mb-2\">Add</button>\n                            </div>\n                        </form>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"modal-footer\">\n                        <form class=\"form-inline flex-fill\" action=\"\" id=\"order_form\">\n                            <div class=\"flex-fill\">\n                                <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-sm btn-danger\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\">Back to Menu</button>\n                                <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn-sm btn-primary pull-right\">Place Order</button>\n                            </div>\n                        </form>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"row menu-lists\">\n            <div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n                <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs nav-justified\" id=\"menuTabs\" role=\"tablist\">\n                    <li class=\"nav-item\" role=\"presentation\">\n                        <button class=\"nav-link active\" id=\"espresso-tab\" data-bs-toggle=\"tab\"\n                                data-bs-target=\"#espresso\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\"\n                                aria-controls=\"espresso\" aria-selected=\"true\">BARISTA</button>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"nav-item\" role=\"presentation\">\n                        <button class=\"nav-link\" id=\"bakery-tab\" data-bs-toggle=\"tab\"\n                                data-bs-target=\"#bakery\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\"\n                                aria-controls=\"bakery\" aria-selected=\"false\">BAKERY</button>\n                    </li>\n                </ul>\n                <div class=\"tab-content\">\n                    <div class=\"tab-pane fade show active\" id=\"espresso\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"espresso-tab\">\n                        <div class=\"row\">\n                            <div class=\"col-xs-12 col-md-6\">\n                                <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                                    <div class=\"name-price-wrap\">\n                                        <div class=\"name pull-left\"><h6>Coffee (black)</h6></div>\n                                        <div class=\"price pull-right\">\n                                            <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn-sm btn-primary\" data-bs-toggle=\"modal\" data-bs-target=\"#myModal\" data-whatever=\"COFFEE_BLACK\" data-item_type=\"beverage\" data-item_price=\"3.50\" data-display_name=\"Coffee (black)\">Add</button>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"desc\"><p>a full cup of coffee</p></div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                                    <div class=\"name-price-wrap\">\n                                        <div class=\"name pull-left\"><h6>Coffee (with room)</h6></div>\n                                        <div class=\"price pull-right\">\n                                            <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn-sm btn-primary\" data-bs-toggle=\"modal\" data-bs-target=\"#myModal\" data-whatever=\"COFFEE_WITH_ROOM\" data-item_type=\"beverage\" data-item_price=\"3.50\" data-display_name=\"Coffee (with room)\">Add</button>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"desc\"><p>a cup of coffee with room for cream or milk</p></div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                                    <div class=\"name-price-wrap\">\n                                        <div class=\"name pull-left\"><h6>Espresso - $3.25</h6></div>\n                                        <div class=\"price pull-right\">\n                                            <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn-sm btn-primary\" data-bs-toggle=\"modal\" data-bs-target=\"#myModal\" data-whatever=\"ESPRESSO\" data-item_type=\"beverage\" data-item_price=\"4.00\" data-display_name=\"Espresso\">Add</button>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"desc\"><p>espresso served with seltzer water</p></div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                                    <div class=\"name-price-wrap\">\n                                        <div class=\"name pull-left\"><h6>Espresso (Double) - $4.25</h6></div>\n                                        <div class=\"price pull-right\">\n                                            <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn-sm btn-primary\" data-bs-toggle=\"modal\" data-bs-target=\"#myModal\" data-whatever=\"ESPRESSO_DOUBLE\" data-item_type=\"beverage\" data-item_price=\"5.25\" data-display_name=\"Double Espresso\">Add</button>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"desc\"><p>2 shots of espresso</p></div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                                    <div class=\"name-price-wrap\">\n                                        <div class=\"name pull-left\"><h6>Cappuccino - $3.75</h6></div>\n                                        <div class=\"price pull-right\">\n                                            <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn-sm btn-primary\" data-bs-toggle=\"modal\" data-bs-target=\"#myModal\" data-whatever=\"CAPPUCCINO\" data-item_type=\"beverage\" data-item_price=\"3.75\" data-display_name=\"Cappuccino\">Add</button>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"desc\"><p>espresso + 4 oz steamed milk</p></div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"col-xs-12 col-md-6\">\n                                <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                                    <div class=\"name-price-wrap\">\n                                        <div class=\"name pull-left\"><h6>Croissant - $4.00</h6></div>\n                                        <div class=\"price pull-right\">\n                                            <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn-sm btn-primary\" data-bs-toggle=\"modal\" data-bs-target=\"#myModal\" data-whatever=\"CROISSANT\" data-item_type=\"kitchen\" data-item_price=\"3.00\" data-display_name=\"Butter Croissant\">Add</button>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"desc\"><p>fresh baked butter croissant</p></div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                                    <div class=\"name-price-wrap\">\n                                        <div class=\"name pull-left\"><h6>Chocolate Croissant - $4.00</h6></div>\n                                        <div class=\"price pull-right\">\n                                            <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn-sm btn-primary\" data-bs-toggle=\"modal\" data-bs-target=\"#myModal\" data-whatever=\"CROISSANT_CHOCOLATE\" data-item_type=\"kitchen\" data-item_price=\"3.25\" data-display_name=\"Chocolate Croissant\">Add</button>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"desc\"><p>fresh baked chocolate croissant</p></div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                                    <div class=\"name-price-wrap\">\n                                        <div class=\"name pull-left\"><h6>Muffin - $3.25</h6></div>\n                                        <div class=\"price pull-right\">\n                                            <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn-sm btn-primary\" data-bs-toggle=\"modal\" data-bs-target=\"#myModal\" data-whatever=\"MUFFIN\" data-item_type=\"kitchen\" data-item_price=\"3.50\" data-display_name=\"Muffin of the Day\">Add</button>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"desc\"><p>blueberry muffin</p></div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                                    <div class=\"name-price-wrap\">\n                                        <div class=\"name pull-left\"><h6>Cakepop - $2.25</h6></div>\n                                        <div class=\"price pull-right\">\n                                            <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn-sm btn-primary\" data-bs-toggle=\"modal\" data-bs-target=\"#myModal\" data-whatever=\"CAKEPOP\" data-item_type=\"kitchen\" data-item_price=\"2.50\" data-display_name=\"Cakepop\">Add</button>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"desc\"><p>chocolate cake with strawberry frosting</p></div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"tab-pane fade\" id=\"bakery\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"bakery-tab\">\n                        <div class=\"row\">\n                            <div class=\"col-xs-12 col-md-12\">\n                                <p>Additional bakery items coming soon!</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n<span class=\"anchor\" id=\"statusboard\"></span>\n<section class=\"statusboard\">\n    <div class=\"container padding-2x\">\n        <div class=\"row text-wrap\">\n            <div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n                <h3 class=\"text-center\">Orders</h3>\n                <hr/>\n                <p class=\"text-center\">Check Here for Your Order Status</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n                <table class=\"table table-lg table-striped\">\n                    <thead class=\"thead-dark\">\n                    <tr>\n                        <th style=\"width:30%\">Customer</th>\n                        <th style=\"width:30%\">Item</th>\n                        <th style=\"width:20%\">Status</th>\n                        <th style=\"width:20%\">Prepared By</th>\n                    </tr>\n                    </thead>\n                    <tbody>\n                    </tbody>\n                </table>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n<span class=\"anchor\" id=\"team\"></span>\n<span class=\"anchor\" id=\"gallery\"></span>\n<span class=\"anchor\" id=\"contact\"></span>\n\n<section class=\"footer\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-xs-12\">\n                <p class=\"text-center\">Coffee Shop Demo</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n\n<div class=\".d-none\"></div>\n<appvalues id=\"appvalues\"\n           th:attr=\"data-store-id=${storeId},data-stream-url=${streamUrl}\"\n/>\n<script src=\"https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.7.1/jquery.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"/js/jquery.matchHeight.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"/js/jquery.cookie.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"/js/custom.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"/js/cafe.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"/js/wow.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/ekko-lightbox/5.3.0/ekko-lightbox.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"/js/toastr.js\"></script>\n<script>\n    new WOW().init();\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1040,"cache_read_input_tokens":102473,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1040,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":5436},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a1c50a88-828f-43a6-8dbe-524f630482b2","uuid":"676f0a14-5b3b-4307-8bb9-23e7ea44ed83"}
